1
00:00:14,809 --> 00:00:20,247
<i>Connecting old words</i>
<i>that have been used up</i>

2
00:00:21,082 --> 00:00:28,989
<i>I just want to convey</i>
<i>my simple thoughts</i>

3
00:00:29,056 --> 00:00:34,426
<i>That day's faint wind blows away</i>

4
00:00:34,495 --> 00:00:38,556
<i>at the castle ruins of yesterday</i>

5
00:00:39,800 --> 00:00:44,703
<i>I'll laugh with you</i>
<i>and live for the moment</i>

6
00:00:45,439 --> 00:00:52,345
<i>Still that incident</i>
<i>will continue to trouble you, right?</i>

7
00:00:53,748 --> 00:00:57,240
<i>That's why it must be good bye</i>

8
00:00:57,318 --> 00:01:04,281
<i>Leaving nothing behind,</i>
<i>let us share what is left</i>

9
00:01:04,358 --> 00:01:11,423
<i>In time, we'll realize</i>
<i>that it was everything</i>

10
00:01:11,499 --> 00:01:18,166
<i>And sadness will touch our cheeks,</i>
<i>creating a river of tears</i>

11
00:01:18,639 --> 00:01:28,139
<i>Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex</i>
<i>and melting away</i>

12
00:01:36,034 --> 00:01:37,501
I'm counting on you, Choji!

13
00:01:37,969 --> 00:01:38,663
Yeah!

14
00:01:40,705 --> 00:01:42,673
Expansion Jutsu!

15
00:01:43,675 --> 00:01:45,973
All right, let's go!

16
00:01:53,485 --> 00:01:55,749
Human Boulder!

17
00:02:19,311 --> 00:02:20,107
What?!

18
00:02:29,387 --> 00:02:35,257
Choji... You are awesome, after all!

19
00:02:38,129 --> 00:02:44,034
<i>Full Throttle Power!</i>
<i>Choji, Ablaz e!</i>

20
00:03:00,452 --> 00:03:03,387
They got away from
my Barrier Ninjutsu...

21
00:03:08,293 --> 00:03:10,318
He's the only one here.

22
00:03:11,529 --> 00:03:14,123
Seems like the others went ahead.

23
00:03:16,301 --> 00:03:16,892
Yeah.

24
00:03:18,169 --> 00:03:19,693
They're not around
here anymore.

25
00:03:20,271 --> 00:03:23,729
Damn... Just when we thought
we caught up.

26
00:03:35,453 --> 00:03:37,751
Everybody, you did well...

27
00:03:39,958 --> 00:03:41,687
for some losers.

28
00:03:41,793 --> 00:03:42,725
What?!

29
00:03:42,794 --> 00:03:44,284
Who are you calling losers?!

30
00:03:46,598 --> 00:03:48,361
Once we're out, it's our battle to win!

31
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,898
I-I will do it!

32
00:03:51,069 --> 00:03:52,229
Wait you two!

33
00:03:54,606 --> 00:03:57,131
It's dangerous to fight them
head on right now!

34
00:03:57,542 --> 00:04:00,443
We tore through the barrier!
We can do this!

35
00:04:04,416 --> 00:04:05,405
Tunneling Fang!

36
00:04:08,253 --> 00:04:09,652
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

37
00:04:10,855 --> 00:04:11,879
- Take this!
- Take this!

38
00:04:16,661 --> 00:04:19,289
You guys are my meal!

39
00:04:19,564 --> 00:04:20,360
Darn it!

40
00:04:21,666 --> 00:04:22,826
Shoulder Charge!

41
00:04:24,502 --> 00:04:25,469
Knee Lift!

42
00:04:28,973 --> 00:04:31,100
Not even good enough for an appetizer!

43
00:04:32,477 --> 00:04:35,537
Be careful everyone!
Another tricky one is coming!

44
00:04:40,685 --> 00:04:43,153
Earth Style Barrier:
Earth Dome Prison!

45
00:04:44,322 --> 00:04:45,619
Expansion Jutsu!

46
00:04:48,293 --> 00:04:49,920
Human Boulder!

47
00:05:00,705 --> 00:05:01,501
Damn!

48
00:05:02,073 --> 00:05:03,404
Such useless acts...

49
00:05:08,646 --> 00:05:09,704
There's no time.

50
00:05:11,316 --> 00:05:13,147
We're going to split into two here!

51
00:05:14,452 --> 00:05:15,612
Why?!

52
00:05:17,188 --> 00:05:18,314
I see...

53
00:05:27,499 --> 00:05:31,663
Even at 5 against 1,
with our Chakras taken away,

54
00:05:31,736 --> 00:05:33,863
he's not someone we can
easily defeat...

55
00:05:34,639 --> 00:05:38,166
If we take our time,
Sasuke will pass the borders.

56
00:05:39,544 --> 00:05:43,412
If that happens, we won't be able
to handle this on our own.

57
00:05:47,352 --> 00:05:49,411
So we split up...
one team to stop him

58
00:05:49,487 --> 00:05:51,614
and one to go after Sasuke, right?

59
00:05:52,056 --> 00:05:55,514
Yeah. The sub leader is going
to be you, Neji.

60
00:06:14,345 --> 00:06:15,505
I found them!

61
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:19,480
Neji! Take Kiba and Choji,
and go after Sasuke!

62
00:06:19,851 --> 00:06:20,545
Got it!

63
00:06:23,521 --> 00:06:24,579
This guy...

64
00:06:24,756 --> 00:06:27,054
Naruto and I will handle!

65
00:06:27,492 --> 00:06:30,325
Are you going to put
the Shadow Paralysis Jutsu on me again?

66
00:06:31,162 --> 00:06:32,652
Such a foolish Jutsu.

67
00:06:32,931 --> 00:06:35,832
I don't need to see that kind of
street performance more than once!

68
00:06:36,668 --> 00:06:41,799
And who was it that got tricked
by that street performance earlier?

69
00:07:07,065 --> 00:07:07,997
He disappeared?!

70
00:07:09,734 --> 00:07:10,530
Behind us!

71
00:07:21,546 --> 00:07:23,912
Earth Style: Sphere of Graves!

72
00:07:24,048 --> 00:07:25,174
He's nuts!

73
00:07:41,065 --> 00:07:43,363
Be careful!
There's another one coming!

74
00:07:49,173 --> 00:07:51,300
You are the platoon leader,
if I'm not mistaken.

75
00:07:52,777 --> 00:07:55,769
You sure do suffer
when you have a stupid leader.

76
00:07:56,281 --> 00:07:57,612
You underlings!

77
00:07:59,417 --> 00:08:01,612
A stupid leader like this...

78
00:08:01,686 --> 00:08:03,621
I'll get rid of for you!

79
00:08:03,621 --> 00:08:06,681
Expansion Jutsu! Human Boulder!

80
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:11,221
Thanks! Choji...

81
00:08:11,829 --> 00:08:15,424
Why? Wasting my good intentions...

82
00:08:20,104 --> 00:08:24,336
If the leader is stupid,
then I guess the subordinates are losers.

83
00:08:26,010 --> 00:08:30,777
Well... I'll kill you losers
before you suffer

84
00:08:30,848 --> 00:08:34,147
working under
a glum shadow lover like him!

85
00:08:34,519 --> 00:08:37,044
Darn, darn! Babbling on like that!

86
00:08:37,121 --> 00:08:38,713
I will!

87
00:08:38,790 --> 00:08:39,654
He's mine!

88
00:08:41,292 --> 00:08:44,261
I will... take care of him!

89
00:08:47,565 --> 00:08:48,429
Choji...

90
00:08:48,633 --> 00:08:49,827
What are you saying?!

91
00:08:50,001 --> 00:08:52,469
He's not the kind of guy
you can handle on your own!

92
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:54,064
I <i>will</i> do it!

93
00:08:54,672 --> 00:08:56,572
Choji... you...

94
00:09:02,013 --> 00:09:04,914
Shikamaru...
Take these Food Pills for everyone...

95
00:09:06,017 --> 00:09:08,315
Choji... You are not...

96
00:09:09,454 --> 00:09:12,651
That's right.
I have that secret weapon of mine.

97
00:09:13,591 --> 00:09:15,024
But Choji, that is!

98
00:09:18,029 --> 00:09:21,863
Huh... Losers, I won't let you
have your way!

99
00:09:21,966 --> 00:09:22,830
He's coming!

100
00:09:23,368 --> 00:09:25,962
I'll get rid of you all here!

101
00:09:27,672 --> 00:09:28,934
Go, everyone!

102
00:09:33,077 --> 00:09:36,069
<i>Pills of three colors?</i>
<i>They're not Food Pills.</i>

103
00:09:36,414 --> 00:09:37,346
<i>What are they?</i>

104
00:09:37,515 --> 00:09:40,006
<i>First... Spinach Pill!</i>

105
00:09:40,618 --> 00:09:42,381
Get out of the way! Loser!

106
00:09:47,291 --> 00:09:50,260
<i>Impossible... He stopped me?!</i>

107
00:09:50,628 --> 00:09:53,995
Shikamaru, take everybody and go!

108
00:09:54,332 --> 00:09:55,196
Choji...

109
00:09:55,767 --> 00:09:58,998
What did we gather for?

110
00:09:59,637 --> 00:10:04,768
If we lose Sasuke,
then we will end up like he said...

111
00:10:05,109 --> 00:10:08,738
The stupid leader and his losers!

112
00:10:14,619 --> 00:10:17,782
You better catch up with us, Choji!

113
00:10:17,955 --> 00:10:18,649
Yeah.

114
00:10:19,424 --> 00:10:21,517
Everybody, go!

115
00:10:21,893 --> 00:10:23,520
All right! Let's go, everyone!

116
00:10:23,861 --> 00:10:24,850
- Yeah!
- Right!

117
00:10:30,735 --> 00:10:31,667
<i>Choji...</i>

118
00:10:33,404 --> 00:10:37,864
I'm going to get rid of you quick
and get rid of those guys too!

119
00:10:38,576 --> 00:10:40,874
It won't be that easy...

120
00:10:56,327 --> 00:10:57,316
<i>What?!</i>

121
00:11:09,507 --> 00:11:11,338
I will...

122
00:11:16,314 --> 00:11:17,611
...stop you!

123
00:11:37,595 --> 00:11:39,620
A parting gift from Choji...
Eat it!

124
00:11:39,797 --> 00:11:40,525
Yeah!

125
00:11:41,265 --> 00:11:42,755
Thanks, Choji...

126
00:11:45,369 --> 00:11:46,097
Kiba!

127
00:11:47,271 --> 00:11:48,101
Thanks!

128
00:11:49,006 --> 00:11:52,772
Shikamaru...
That pill that Choji took earlier...

129
00:11:53,010 --> 00:11:55,137
It seemed like some sort
of trump card,

130
00:11:56,113 --> 00:11:57,273
but does he have a chance to win?

131
00:11:58,115 --> 00:12:00,879
He said that he has a secret weapon.

132
00:12:01,552 --> 00:12:07,650
He brought the Akimichi clan's
ultimate secret pills on this mission...

133
00:12:09,260 --> 00:12:12,388
These are the Triad Colored Pills
of green, yellow, and red.

134
00:12:12,463 --> 00:12:15,455
If you take it,
you can gain explosive powers.

135
00:12:16,834 --> 00:12:21,168
The energy that each pill
contains is enormous!

136
00:12:21,539 --> 00:12:25,270
I see! I see!
So that's why he was so confident!

137
00:12:26,177 --> 00:12:30,511
<i>But... there's always a side effect</i>
<i>to any pills that work too well.</i>

138
00:12:42,326 --> 00:12:45,853
<i>Damn... I didn't think it would hurt</i>
<i>so much with just the Spinach Pill.</i>

139
00:12:50,334 --> 00:12:53,497
<i>I hope that Choji can settle it</i>
<i>with just the green pill.</i>

140
00:12:54,305 --> 00:12:57,706
<i>Don't take the red one,</i>
<i>no matter what, Choji.</i>

141
00:13:04,248 --> 00:13:06,182
<i>I'm going to finish you at once!</i>

142
00:13:19,563 --> 00:13:20,825
Expansion Jutsu!

143
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:32,400
Spiky Human Boulder.

144
00:13:42,052 --> 00:13:44,247
<i>He raised the rotational</i>
<i>and destructive power</i>

145
00:13:44,321 --> 00:13:46,221
<i>by using the Kunai Knives as spikes!</i>

146
00:13:52,196 --> 00:13:54,494
Earth Style: Terra Shield.

147
00:14:03,574 --> 00:14:04,472
What?!

148
00:14:27,531 --> 00:14:28,759
<i>I-I did</i> it... <i>?

149
00:14:36,206 --> 00:14:38,868
Yeah. That's what I was thinking too.

150
00:14:39,376 --> 00:14:41,367
Akamaru...
What is he saying?

151
00:14:41,745 --> 00:14:44,270
You know that Akamaru
can tell the strength of the enemy

152
00:14:44,348 --> 00:14:45,610
just by the smell, right?

153
00:14:46,483 --> 00:14:52,149
He's worried if Choji is going to be able
to handle that monster with just the pills.

154
00:14:54,892 --> 00:14:55,790
True...

155
00:14:56,160 --> 00:14:58,253
If we were to assess
the situation objectively,

156
00:14:58,329 --> 00:15:00,695
that giant's ability is unknown...

157
00:15:01,498 --> 00:15:04,865
The possibility of Choji being able
to defeat him might be close to zero.

158
00:15:05,402 --> 00:15:06,300
But...

159
00:15:08,572 --> 00:15:10,096
That is how battle is...

160
00:15:20,684 --> 00:15:22,709
Don't get carried away, loser!

161
00:15:24,655 --> 00:15:26,486
Shatter Palm!

162
00:15:37,835 --> 00:15:39,200
Did you know?

163
00:15:39,403 --> 00:15:41,496
When there's a group of people
of five or so,

164
00:15:41,572 --> 00:15:43,597
there's always one loser.

165
00:15:44,475 --> 00:15:47,467
That person is always made fun of...

166
00:15:48,012 --> 00:15:49,604
and when it comes down to it,

167
00:15:49,680 --> 00:15:52,240
they'll just toss that person
aside like a pawn.

168
00:15:54,585 --> 00:15:56,280
I'm talking about you!

169
00:16:00,691 --> 00:16:06,152
<i>Choji. All you want to do is eat.</i>
<i>You should train some at least!</i>

170
00:16:07,331 --> 00:16:12,064
<i>You get teased because you're like that.</i>
<i>You're just a-</i>

171
00:16:12,369 --> 00:16:14,769
<i>You said somebody exceptional, right?</i>

172
00:16:14,838 --> 00:16:16,703
<i>Shouldn't we ask Shino or somebody?!</i>

173
00:16:17,574 --> 00:16:21,408
<i>This guy is useless too...</i>

174
00:16:32,790 --> 00:16:33,757
<i>That is true...</i>

175
00:16:34,925 --> 00:16:37,519
<i>No matter how hard I try on my own...</i>

176
00:16:39,196 --> 00:16:40,026
I...

177
00:16:48,472 --> 00:16:50,599
Seems like I hit it right on the nose.

178
00:16:52,910 --> 00:16:55,743
Seems like the Leaf is lacking in people,

179
00:16:55,813 --> 00:16:59,442
seeing that they pick a loser
like you to be on the pursuit team.

180
00:17:03,654 --> 00:17:05,645
Why don't we finish this up already?!

181
00:17:09,326 --> 00:17:10,918
Knee Lift!

182
00:17:11,028 --> 00:17:12,290
Shoulder Charge!

183
00:17:14,198 --> 00:17:16,996
Huh! You really are a loser to the end!

184
00:17:17,935 --> 00:17:21,666
Your high spirit didn't last long at all,
only at the beginning!

185
00:17:22,439 --> 00:17:24,703
You really are the ideal loser!

186
00:17:27,678 --> 00:17:32,012
A loser like you shouldn't have come
to a place like this!

187
00:17:32,649 --> 00:17:36,107
You should blame your stupid leader
for choosing you!

188
00:17:38,689 --> 00:17:39,849
<i>Shikamaru...</i>

189
00:17:40,424 --> 00:17:43,393
Neji's right. It's how a battle is.

190
00:17:44,695 --> 00:17:47,220
From the start, this mission
wasn't for recreation.

191
00:17:48,098 --> 00:17:49,429
It's life or death.

192
00:17:50,467 --> 00:17:52,230
Hey Shikamaru...

193
00:17:53,337 --> 00:17:55,305
I already anticipated the worst scenario

194
00:17:55,372 --> 00:17:58,170
in which we would be fighting
separately on our own.

195
00:17:58,575 --> 00:17:59,633
And at this point,

196
00:17:59,710 --> 00:18:02,406
if we're not prepared for
"one person, one kill,"

197
00:18:02,479 --> 00:18:04,310
we might not be able
to catch up to Sasuke.

198
00:18:12,589 --> 00:18:16,548
Choji is a good guy,
but he doesn't have the confidence.

199
00:18:17,127 --> 00:18:20,858
He thinks that
he's the weakest of all of us.

200
00:18:21,565 --> 00:18:24,728
He actually is weak.
Anybody can see that.

201
00:18:25,402 --> 00:18:29,964
That's why he was the first to
stay behind to try to be useful.

202
00:18:31,542 --> 00:18:33,032
Just as I thought...

203
00:18:35,913 --> 00:18:36,811
<i>But...</i>

204
00:18:51,895 --> 00:18:54,989
<i>Choji and I have worked as a team</i>
<i>for many years,</i>

205
00:18:55,699 --> 00:18:58,099
<i>so coordinating with him</i>
<i>is easiest for me.</i>

206
00:18:58,535 --> 00:19:00,469
<i>But Shikamaru...</i>

207
00:19:15,886 --> 00:19:20,482
<i>But, if we fight against each other,</i>
<i>you might be stronger.</i>

208
00:19:20,557 --> 00:19:24,084
<i>I might have given up fighting</i>
<i>against you too.</i>

209
00:19:25,295 --> 00:19:27,058
<i>And you're you...</i>

210
00:19:29,700 --> 00:19:30,724
<i>But...</i>

211
00:19:33,737 --> 00:19:36,638
<i>Shikamaru... has always...</i>

212
00:19:39,943 --> 00:19:43,606
<i>Shikamaru has always</i>
<i>believed in</i> me...

213
00:19:44,748 --> 00:19:47,182
<i>Choji... are you ready?!</i>

214
00:19:50,988 --> 00:19:54,389
<i>He believed that I was really strong!</i>

215
00:20:01,298 --> 00:20:04,392
<i>That's why he left it up to me alone!</i>

216
00:20:12,175 --> 00:20:13,142
Just as I thought...

217
00:20:15,212 --> 00:20:20,411
So everybody thinks that...
But... I know...

218
00:20:23,921 --> 00:20:27,322
More than myself or Neji
or any of us here...

219
00:20:27,891 --> 00:20:29,188
He <i>is</i> stronger!

220
00:20:32,129 --> 00:20:35,530
And... I believe it.

221
00:20:36,733 --> 00:20:39,429
Oh? Pretty impressive Chakra.

222
00:20:41,071 --> 00:20:44,598
But... it's a far cry
from being a main dish...

223
00:20:48,111 --> 00:20:49,476
Let's go, fatso!

224
00:20:50,614 --> 00:20:52,411
Don't YOU say that!

225
00:20:53,283 --> 00:20:55,513
Partial Expansion Jutsu!

226
00:21:13,003 --> 00:21:20,102
<i>Once in a long while, once in a while</i>

227
00:21:20,243 --> 00:21:25,772
<i>The remnants of a person</i>
<i>broken by dreams</i>

228
00:21:25,949 --> 00:21:31,012
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

229
00:21:34,324 --> 00:21:41,321
<i>Clinging to the Divine,</i>
<i>clinging to Buddha</i>

230
00:21:41,398 --> 00:21:46,927
<i>The remnants of a person crying</i>

231
00:21:47,337 --> 00:21:50,898
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

232
00:21:52,576 --> 00:21:55,636
<i>Rendezvous with a happy dance circle</i>

233
00:21:55,712 --> 00:21:59,512
<i>This is my victory pose, round and around</i>
<i>(round around)</i>

234
00:21:59,850 --> 00:22:02,785
<i>Shake shake shake</i>
<i>Let's look</i>

235
00:22:02,853 --> 00:22:06,983
<i>With a bye bye rhythm that never ends</i>

236
00:22:16,166 --> 00:22:21,263
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

237
00:22:23,206 --> 00:22:26,471
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

238
00:22:26,877 --> 00:22:30,074
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

239
00:22:30,347 --> 00:22:34,340
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

240
00:22:39,523 --> 00:22:41,491
I can't move because of the pain.

241
00:22:41,658 --> 00:22:44,252
I didn't think the side effects
of the secret pill would be strong.

242
00:22:44,961 --> 00:22:48,362
What do I do?
I only have one more pill.

243
00:22:48,732 --> 00:22:53,396
But if I take it, if I take it,
I will... surely...

244
00:22:54,604 --> 00:22:58,870
Next time: "Good-bye Old Friend!
